Even two years after the release of the open-world game "Elden Ring", the hype remains unbroken. The recently released DLC "Shadow of the Erdtree", in which players once again have to deal with a number of tough bosses, is likely to have contributed to this. But that's by no means all, as the creators have now expressed their interest in a movie adaptation of "Elden Ring".
